WEBVTT

00:00:00.735 --> 00:00:02.137
[narrator]
<i>First you fall in love.</i>

00:00:02.171 --> 00:00:03.574
<i>Then you confess it.</i>

00:00:03.608 --> 00:00:09.085
<i>Ask anyone, and they’ll say</i>
<i>this is a wonderful thing.</i>

00:00:09.118 --> 00:00:10.622
<i>But they are so very wrong.</i>

00:00:10.655 --> 00:00:12.024
[fast‐forwarding]
<i>Even with the cutest...</i>

00:00:12.057 --> 00:00:13.794
<i>...side that takes...</i>
<i>...winner and a loser‐‐</i>

00:00:13.828 --> 00:00:15.765
[normal] <i>Love is no game!</i>

00:00:15.798 --> 00:00:17.134
<i>It’s war!</i>

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:25.752
<i>Whoever gives their heart first</i>
<i>will be conquered.</i>

00:00:27.856 --> 00:00:30.027
[Japanese music playing]

00:02:00.842 --> 00:02:01.744
Hmm?

00:02:03.279 --> 00:02:05.250
Where’d this come from?

00:02:05.283 --> 00:02:07.956
Oh, the principal
confiscated that magazine

00:02:07.989 --> 00:02:09.125
from a student here,

00:02:09.158 --> 00:02:10.862
