in a school,

00:02:10.895 --> 00:02:12.064
so we should toss it.

00:02:12.097 --> 00:02:13.199
It’s weird, though.

00:02:13.233 --> 00:02:15.103
Why didn’t he
just trash it himself?

00:02:15.137 --> 00:02:17.709
I wonder why he thinks
it doesn’t belong here.

00:02:17.742 --> 00:02:19.680
[wails]

00:02:21.015 --> 00:02:22.251
‐ I’m scarred!
‐ [buzzer]

00:02:22.284 --> 00:02:25.625
No! I mean I’m scared
for the future of our country!

00:02:25.658 --> 00:02:28.363
[Shirogane] <i>Why is</i>
<i>she freaking out?</i>

00:02:28.396 --> 00:02:29.766
<i>Are there naked chicks</i>
<i>in that thing?</i>

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:32.471
[narrator] <i>And suddenly</i>
<i>Shirogane is very interested.</i>

00:02:32.505 --> 00:02:34.676
‐ [murmuring]
‐ What’s the fuss about?

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:36.112
A survey asks people

00:02:36.145 --> 00:02:38.149
how old they were
for their first time,

00:02:38.183 --> 00:02:41.489
