<i>wasn’t part of her upbringing.</i>

00:07:51.409 --> 00:07:52.578
<i>Far from it.</i>

00:07:53.514 --> 00:07:55.618
<i>She was taught</i>
<i>that people kiss,</i>

00:07:55.651 --> 00:07:57.889
